title: Cool Mafia mod!!!!
description:
This is a very cool program that i found on the internet...

I take no credit for the creation of this program...
i only take credit for uploading it..

I love the game mafia and i just recently beat it and 
wanted to have something else to do.

The install instructions are in the folder.
so just read the instructions carefully and have fun
with all the new features and stuff!!!!!

And i also included a the map of Mafia and a map of 
where the freeride extreme people are located (because 
used to always have some trouble with finding them)..lol.

remeber to always seed as I will be always seeding any 
and all file(s) that i upload....

ENJOY!!!!!!!

PS:  Please come back and let me know what you think about it!!!!
